24
00:01:43,132 --> 00:01:48,670
Cyber physical systems have their
own specific security issues.

25
00:01:48,670 --> 00:01:51,220
This is because of their
special characteristics.

26
00:01:52,500 --> 00:01:57,010
First of all,
as they are involving physical processes,

27
00:01:57,010 --> 00:02:00,109
they are tightly coupled with
their physical environments.

28
00:02:01,310 --> 00:02:04,450
