In a system which carries out autonomous
operations through its actuators,

77
00:06:20,884 --> 00:06:26,464
it is of key importance to make sure
that all actuations are authorized and

78
00:06:26,464 --> 00:06:30,160
according to the latest
policies of the system.

79
00:06:33,040 --> 00:06:37,600
Feedback loops play an important role
in cyber physical system control.

80
00:06:39,610 --> 00:06:42,320
A system's embedded intelligence and

81
00:06:42,320 --> 00:06:47,629
ability to learn are largely based
on feedback of its actuations.

82
00:06:48,810 --> 00:06:53,590
Therefore the feedback data needs to
be appropriately protected against

83
