tampering attempts.

84
00:06:57,336 --> 00:07:02,029
Finally, the system may have some
application specific security

85
00:07:02,029 --> 00:07:07,990
requirements, depending on the nature of
the applications running in the system.

86
00:07:10,890 --> 00:07:15,540
Cyber physical systems have both
physical and cyber aspects that

87
00:07:15,540 --> 00:07:19,890
need to be taken into account when
designing security counter measures.

88
00:07:21,410 --> 00:07:26,130
In developing security solutions for
cyber physical systems,

89
00:07:26,130 --> 00:07:29,850
we need to keep in mind that
attacks can also be indirect

90
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:35,350
meaning that they can aim to
affect the physical environment in

91
00:07:35,350 --> 00:07:39,850
such a way that data coming
